title: 134: LaMarr Woodley joins for scouting report, bad bodies
itunes:title: 134: LaMarr Woodley joins for scouting report, bad bodies
description:
Former NFL linebacker LaMarr Woodley joins former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks to discuss more bad bodies, good players and his new show on NFL Network, Tackle My Ride. DJ also reminds Woodley of his college scouting report before the duo make their football picks for the weekend.
